.\" suika3-run.1 - Suika3 manpage
.TH SUIKA3 1 "April 2026" "Suika3 1.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
suika3-launcher \- Run Suika3 from GUI
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B suika3-launcher

.SH DESCRIPTION
The
.B Suika3
is a cross-platform scripting VM for 2D games and visual novels.

When invoked,
.B suika3-launcher
starts the Suika3 launcer.

If a file or a directory is specified as a command line argument,
it starts the game in the specified place.

